WEBVTT

00:09:28.993 --> 00:09:33.790
which was that the better-off schools
or better-off people

00:09:33.814 --> 00:09:35.854
or better-off countries would have it,

00:09:35.878 --> 00:09:37.830
and you'd actually accentuate

00:09:37.854 --> 00:09:41.783
that it was such an amazing tool
for curiosity and learning

00:09:41.807 --> 00:09:45.841
that we just needed to make sure
it was available to everyone.

00:09:46.595 --> 00:09:50.302
The idea that in some respects,

00:09:50.326 --> 00:09:51.945
it could be used in a way --

00:09:51.969 --> 00:09:54.329
or the effect in terms of overuse

00:09:54.353 --> 00:09:56.871
or people isolating off into groups --

00:09:56.895 --> 00:10:02.086
that that would come back into the realm
of how people think about facts